Goodness Nwachukwu (onye amụrụ n'abalị isii n'ọnwa Ọktoba n'afọ 1998) bụ onye Naijiria na-eme egwuregwu nke na-ahụ maka discus. O meriri nrite ọla edo naDiscus umunwanyi F42 na 2022 Commonwealth Games, na-etinye ihe ndekọ ụwa ọhụrụ maka ọzụzụ nke 36.56m. Ọ mebiri ihe ndekọ ụwa nke 32.95m, nke e debere na  para egwuregwu Ụwa na Nnukwu ihe nritena nke 2021 na Tunis.
